{"tid":1508440,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"咪撚玩fake new，要玩就玩白色恐佈","createTime":"2019-08-26T13:58:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T14:14:43.000Z","uid":290410,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"98ae1729dd198a5822fc529ab2f385b608b15766","tid":1508440,"uid":290410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T13:58:17.000Z","msg":"佢地識用篤灰玩白色恐佈，其實我地可以借力打力。對付依樣冇腦既大家唔洗慳咁多口水，公司高層基本上都係藍絲，既得利益者。局外人點出聲都唔會有用，大部份香港人亦都唔會齊上齊落。但係將依啲藍絲變成佢地最憎既人就係最好既報復。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">點變</span></span><br />\n大家唔好高估藍絲，佢地只需要一張cap圖， 你話佢係佢就已經信。 大家可以睇下呢個tg group，當然手足有能力PS緊係最好。<br />\n父母搵仔女（逃犯條例）<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/yeeseelostandfound\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyeeseelostandfound&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrscdEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=7ed13dd3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/yeeseelostandfound</a><br />\n<br />\n佢哋單憑一張facebook cap圖使，甚至一張相已經足夠會報返畀大陸，佢地得點解我地唔得， <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">甚至可以幫佢哋開個facebook</span></span>。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">一黎</span>增加大陸檢查相片既成本，如果過關捉埋佢地就係bonus<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.12339.gov.cn/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.12339.gov.cn%2F&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrscdEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=bb284158\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.12339.gov.cn/</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">二黎</span>拉哂所有人落水，藍絲親戚朋友以至經常返大陸既港豬，鼓勵大家幫啲垃圾藍絲呀伯開Facebook一返佢地親愛既祖國慢慢招呼佢地。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">三黎</span>用大量既訊息去保護返被篤灰既手足，個個都係黃絲既時侯點捉。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">四黎</span> 整返個白色恐佈畀藍絲港豬"},{"pid":"4d04674c6fa657ade6c2b10fe1310b01cab0a718","tid":1508440,"uid":29899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T13:58:39.000Z","msg":"[9．1機場] 文宣集合 2.0<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1507880\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1507880</a><br />\n<br />\n現有文宣集合 (Google Drive)<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.googl